{
  "text": "Deep convolutional neural network, since the breakthrough result in the ImageNet classification challenge [CITATION_1] , has been widely studied [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . It has achieved surprising performance in many other computer vision tasks, including object detection [CITATION_5] , semantic segmentation [CITATION_6] , edge detection [CITATION_7] , and so on.",
  "correct_citation": {
